class DQNTrainer(Callback):
    discount=0.99
    _yb=None
    
    def after_pred(self):
        yb=self.yb[0]
        self._yb=yb
        done_mask=yb['done'].reshape(-1,)
        next_q=learn.model.model(yb['next_state']).max(dim=1).values.reshape(-1,1)
        targets=yb['reward']+next_q*self.discount
        targets[done_mask]=yb[done_mask]['reward']
        q=self.learn.model.model(yb['state'])
        t_q=q.clone()
        t_q[yb['action'].reshape(-1,)]=targets
        self.learn.yb=(t_q,)
        self.learn.pred=q
        
    def before_backward(self): self.learn.yb=self._yb
